                             Early Voting and Absentee
                               Voting Dates for 2002




                              May Election

   02/05/02 First day to accept requests for by mail ballots (including
            inmates)
   04/15/02 Start nursing home voting
   04/16/02 Last day to accept applications from prisoners
   04/17/02 First day for early voting
   04/24/02 Last day to mail prisoners ballots
   04/30/02 Last day to accept a request for an absentee by mail ballot
   04/30/02 Prisoner voting day
   05/02/02 Last day to early vote
   05/02/02 Last day for by mail applications or full info requests

   August Election

   05/03/02 First day to accept requests for by mail ballots
   07/10/02 Start nursing home voting
   07/12/02 First day for early voting
   07/25/02 Last day to accept a request for an absentee by mail ballot
   07/27/02 Last day for early voting
   07/27/02 Last day for by mail applications or full info requests


